title: I mean it’s oil- what do you need to know?
description: OK the only reason I gave it for stars instead of five as it does not have an easy pour spout. Other than that it’s oil no different than any other oil out there that I know of if you could tell me there’s something special about it please let me know. My car has almost 140,000 miles on it. It’s a 2008 Toyota this as a Great price point so I have purchased this oil on a few occasions, and as long as the price point is better than the others, I will continue to purchase it even if a small amount is missed due to the lack of a spout, but then again, I could just buy a funnel
date: Reviewed in the United States on August 4, 2023
